textAnnotations.description:
DEAD MAN TALKING
Hang up and drive. End of conversation.
Cell phones and
safe driving don't
mix. Motorists who
talk on the phone
while driving are
four times more
TALK
likely to be involved
in a crash.
--- Save a Life
Texas Department of Transportation
Fr
